long, sometimes complicated words or

00:00:23.564 --> 00:00:29.115
phrases used in computing, and it,
they're created to make our lives

00:00:29.115 --> 00:00:31.605
easier and our conversations faster.

00:00:32.195 --> 00:00:35.434
Especially when we talk about
all this technical stuff.

00:00:35.915 --> 00:00:41.045
For example, instead of saying central
processing unit again and again, like a

00:00:41.045 --> 00:00:44.360
stuck record, we just say CPU much better.

00:00:44.379 --> 00:00:44.599
No.

00:00:46.230 --> 00:00:47.730
Real world relevance.

