00:07:26.700 --> 00:07:29.195
Understand the question
before moving to explanation.

00:07:31.424 --> 00:07:35.744
The question asks for the full form
of RAM a type of computer memory.

00:07:36.044 --> 00:07:37.724
Let's evaluate our options.

00:07:38.085 --> 00:07:40.364
Read access Memory is incorrect.

00:07:40.755 --> 00:07:43.244
Random access module is also wrong.

00:07:43.575 --> 00:07:47.054
